SUMMARY:🎬 The Secret Agent (2025)
DESCRIPTION:The Secret Agent is a 2025 historical political thriller film written and directed by Kleber Mendonça Filho. It follows Armando, a former professor caught in the political turmoil in the midst of the Brazilian military dictatorship, attempting to flee persecution and resist an authoritarian regime. The supporting cast includes Carlos Francisco, Tânia Maria, Robério Diógenes, Gabriel Leone, Maria Fernanda Cândido, Alice Carvalho, and Udo Kier in his final film role.\nShowtime: 7:00 PM at Peacock Hall\nFree admission\nAuto-synced from rossmoor.com recreation calendar
